{"tid":1115725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為再教育營辯護　中國外交官：不懂普通話還有什麼人權可言","createTime":"2019-04-19T11:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T17:39:22.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"91a53013d6790aaabb7902737d3fab1ef81fa04f","tid":1115725,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-04-19/235568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2019-04-19%2F235568&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSSWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=46280f95\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-04-19/235568</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/236/5cb9703966af5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F236%2F5cb9703966af5.jpg&h=d2b7aaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國駐哈薩克大使張霄。   圖：翻攝自人民網<br />\n<br />\n中國新疆再教育營對於維吾爾人的人權迫害，受到國際社會的關注，同時也備受譴責，中國一名駐哈薩克外交官近日接受採訪時，極力為「再教育營」辯護，強調沒有這一類的設施，只有「職業技能培訓中心」，為的是要將這些人教育好，他更狂言指出，若要成為好人，首先便要學會普通話，若連普通話都不懂，還談什麼人權。<br />\n<br />\n根據《美國之音》報導，中國官媒《環球時報》於16日以「大使講述新疆真相」為題，刊登中國駐哈薩克共和國大使張霄對哈薩克媒體的訪談，張霄談起新疆現狀，重申中國官方立場，強調新疆根本不存在集中營或再教育營等設施，只有「職業技能培訓中心」。<br />\n<br />\n張霄表示，這些培訓中心不是監獄，而是「面向全社會的學校」，而此一機構唯一目的便是「把人教育好，不讓好人變壞人」，他強調，培訓中心沒有「酷刑」，只有對人權的尊重和保護。<br />\n<br />\n然而，究竟要如何成為「好人」？張霄認為，必須要學習國家通用語言及文字，也就是普通話，他狂言指出，「對於一個現代人，如果不會本國通用語言文字，還有什麼人權可言？」"},{"pid":"e168f95559d9a86a4567968ff7ae836b7ded2fe3","tid":1115725,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLy2BP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLy2BP8.png&h=91d426e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90eebd37c4d4224cf226e2f23d4a45ac05f551a9","tid":1115725,"uid":37856,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"崔世安？"},{"pid":"7f52fede4d3f4c9e12431d6b2fb8b3a4df3ed2c2","tid":1115725,"uid":62599,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"地球上既渣滓有好多 特別係強國最多"},{"pid":"39db50edac9baff664ec23899df85bb3c2e42186","tid":1115725,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"即係自爆國家冇人權"},{"pid":"1312fa0d62786447dc39ce0b83730b3cf8696b89","tid":1115725,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"呢個答案其實同D人話晌香港唔講廣東話XXX異曲同功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09b8e70b8fba1b543ad49d2c51548b0c159281d","tid":1115725,"uid":41389,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"順便表達埋香港人無人權囉"},{"pid":"fbf1b8daa4d9cbecb3cfeb88f6875cbab5e18685","tid":1115725,"uid":199957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"外交官咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n係咪又係小學畢業就上位做到而家"},{"pid":"6423c1f3fd6be9f58277f4e66e16108cf57fcc36","tid":1115725,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"毛澤東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa7ae358973387fade0dd77f1bb5936008a8c38","tid":1115725,"uid":44391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:35:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f67e732eb46d735a9b37bb95071dccf89aff528f","tid":1115725,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469b181b5c2d4e1548c1fe21ac073fd8efa39983","tid":1115725,"uid":186692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"講到識支那狗話嘅畜生好有人權咁"},{"pid":"c7a8ca38726c680a064a7b15b5d7ff87d94ac14b","tid":1115725,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim